# Forms (`src/app/features/shared/form`)

1. Model: `*.model.ts` interface for form value.
2. Definition: `export const X = defineForm<Model>()({ mode: 'single'|'stepper', steps: [...] })`.
3. Page: `FormBuilder` group mirrors field keys; pass `[definition]` + `[form]` to `FormPageComponent`.
4. Options: `{ value, labelKey }`; field types: text, email, tel, number, date, password, textarea, select, radio, checkbox, toggle, custom. Optional `autocomplete` on `FieldDef`.
5. Optional `titleKey` / `subtitleKey` on sections and steps — header/labels omitted when unset.
6. Custom blocks: `formFieldKey` / `formSectionKey` / `formStepKey` + `*Template` directives in page HTML.
7. Submit: `form.getRawValue() as Model` (validators on `FormGroup`, not only in def). Pass `[submitDisabled]` to `app-form-page` during async submit (parent owns the signal).

Extend field types in `form-field-renderer` + `fields/form-*-field/`, not ad-hoc duplicate inputs on standard pages.
